!! @LEXNAME@ 
! Present Neg
–Ψ–Ζ+V+Neg+Ind+Prs+Sg1:–Ψ–≥ MatrixVerb_Comparison ;
–Ψ–Ζ+V+Neg+Ind+Prs+Sg2:–Ψ–Ϋ MatrixVerb_Comparison ;
–Ψ–Ζ+V+Neg+Ind+Prs+Sg3:–Ψ–Ζ MatrixVerb_Comparison ;
–Ψ–Ζ+V+Neg+Ind+Prs+Pl1:–Ψ–≥”ß MatrixVerb_Comparison ;
–Ψ–Ζ+V+Neg+Ind+Prs+Pl2:–Ψ–Ϋ”ß MatrixVerb_Comparison ;
