–Ψ–Ζ+V+Neg+Ind+Prs+Pl2:–Ψ–Ϋ”ß–Ι MatrixVerb_Comparison ;
–Ψ–Ζ+V+Neg+Ind+Prs+Pl3:–Ψ–Ζ MatrixVerb_Comparison ;

–Ψ–Ζ+Use/NG+Err/Dial+V+Neg+Ind+Prs+Pl1:–Ψ–≥–Β MatrixVerb_Comparison ;
–Ψ–Ζ+Use/NG+Err/Dial+V+Neg+Ind+Prs+Pl2:–Ψ–Ϋ―ç MatrixVerb_Comparison ;
–Ψ–Ζ+Use/NG+Err/Dial+V+Neg+Ind+Prs+Pl1:–Ψ–≥–Β–Ι MatrixVerb_Comparison ;
–Ψ–Ζ+Use/NG+Err/Dial+V+Neg+Ind+Prs+Pl2:–Ψ–Ϋ―ç–Ι MatrixVerb_Comparison ;

!Past Neg
–Ψ–Ζ+V+Neg+Ind+Prt1+Sg1:―ç–≥ MatrixVerb_Comparison ;
–Ψ–Ζ+V+Neg+Ind+Prt1+Sg2:―ç–Ϋ MatrixVerb_Comparison ;
–Ψ–Ζ+V+Neg+Ind+Prt1+Sg3:―ç–Ζ MatrixVerb_Comparison ;
–Ψ–Ζ+V+Neg+Ind+Prt1+Pl1:―ç–≥ MatrixVerb_Comparison ;
–Ψ–Ζ+V+Neg+Ind+Prt1+Pl2:―ç–Ϋ MatrixVerb_Comparison ;
–Ψ–Ζ+V+Neg+Ind+Prt1+Pl1:―ç–≥”ß MatrixVerb_Comparison ;
–Ψ–Ζ+V+Neg+Ind+Prt1+Pl2:―ç–Ϋ”ß MatrixVerb_Comparison ;
–Ψ–Ζ+V+Neg+Ind+Prt1+Pl3:―ç–Ζ MatrixVerb_Comparison ;
–Ψ–Ζ+Use/NG+Err/Dial+V+Neg+Ind+Prt1+Pl1:―ç–≥–Β MatrixVerb_Comparison ;
–Ψ–Ζ+Use/NG+Err/Dial+V+Neg+Ind+Prt1+Pl2:―ç–Ϋ―ç MatrixVerb_Comparison ;

!Past Neg Err/Dial
–Ψ–Ζ+V+Neg+Ind+Prt1+Sg1+Use/NG+Err/Dial:–Η–≥ MatrixVerb_Comparison ;
–Ψ–Ζ+V+Neg+Ind+Prt1+Sg2+Use/NG+Err/Dial:–Η–Ϋ MatrixVerb_Comparison ;
–Ψ–Ζ+V+Neg+Ind+Prt1+Sg3+Use/NG+Err/Dial:–Η–Ζ MatrixVerb_Comparison ;
–Ψ–Ζ+V+Neg+Ind+Prt1+Pl1+Use/NG+Err/Dial:–Η–≥ MatrixVerb_Comparison ;
–Ψ–Ζ+V+Neg+Ind+Prt1+Pl2+Use/NG+Err/Dial:–Η–Ϋ MatrixVerb_Comparison ;
–Ψ–Ζ+V+Neg+Ind+Prt1+Pl1+Use/NG+Err/Dial:–Η–≥–Β MatrixVerb_Comparison ;
–Ψ–Ζ+V+Neg+Ind+Prt1+Pl2+Use/NG+Err/Dial:–Η–Ϋ―ç MatrixVerb_Comparison ;
–Ψ–Ζ+V+Neg+Ind+Prt1+Pl3+Use/NG+Err/Dial:–Η–Ζ MatrixVerb_Comparison ;
–Ψ–Ζ+Use/NG+Err/Dial+V+Neg+Ind+Prt1+Pl1+Err/Dial:–Η–≥–Β MatrixVerb_Comparison ;
–Ψ–Ζ+Use/NG+Err/Dial+V+Neg+Ind+Prt1+Pl2+Err/Dial:–Η–Ϋ―ç MatrixVerb_Comparison ;

!Imperative
–Ψ–Ζ+V+Neg+Imprt+Sg2:―ç–Ϋ K ;
–Ψ–Ζ+V+Neg+Imprt+Pl2:―ç–Ϋ K ;
–Ψ–Ζ+V+Neg+Imprt+Pl2:―ç–Ϋ”ß K ;
–Ψ–Ζ+V+Neg+Imprt+Pl2:―ç–Ϋ”ß–Ι K ;
–Ψ–Ζ+Use/NG+Err/Dial+V+Neg+Imprt+Pl2:―ç–Ϋ―ç K ;
!A tag is needed to indicate this clitic-like –Μ―΄ segment
–Ψ–Ζ+V+Neg+Imprt+Sg2:―ç–Ϋ–Μ―΄ K ;
–Ψ–Ζ+V+Neg+Imprt+Pl2:―ç–Ϋ–Μ”ß–Ι K ;

!Final
–Φ–Ψ–Ζ+V+Neg+Final+1:–Φ–Ψ–≥ K ; ! –Φ–Β–¥ –Ψ–≥ _so that I/we won't_
–Φ–Ψ–Ζ+V+Neg+Final+2:–Φ–Ψ–Ϋ K ; ! –Φ–Β–¥ –Ψ–Ϋ
–Φ–Ψ–Ζ+V+Neg+Final+3:–Φ–Ψ–Ζ K ; ! –Φ–Β–¥ –Ψ–Ζ

! Negative copula supletive present forms
!–Α–±―É+V+Neg+Cop+Ind+Sg:–Α–±―É K ; ! Aux these are supletive. Past is ―ç–Ζ –≤”ß–≤
!–Α–±―É+V+Neg+Cop+Ind+Pl:–Α–±―É”ß―¹―¨ K ; ! Aux these are supletive. Past is ―ç–Ζ –≤”ß–≤–Ϋ―΄



